text: Piscataquis County is a county located in the U.S. state of Maine. As of the 2020 census, its population was 16,800, making it Maine's least-populous county. Its county seat is Dover-Foxcroft. ==References== Category:Maine counties Category:1838 establishments in the United States Category:19th- century establishments in Maine
